Description: The 'LibOPF' is a framework to develop pattern recognition
        techniques based on optimum-path forests (OPF), João P. Papa
        and Alexandre X. Falcão (2008)
        <doi:10.1007/978-3-540-89639-5_89>, with methods for supervised
        learning and data clustering.
